timelineItems.comment: Delay in match Patrick Nyarko (Chicago Fire) because of an injury.

timelineItems.name: Kai Dambach
timelineItems.text: Nyarko down on the pitch in the 82nd. No one touched him, fell awkwardly going for the ball and rolled in pain. Those are the worst. #DCvCHI

timelineItems.comment: Delay over. They are ready to continue.

timelineItems.text: Nyarko stretchered off, replaced by Ward. Crowd gives him a round of applause. #DCU #DCvCHI
